title: Tarja Turunen - 5 singles
description:
This is a collection of solo singles by the former (the best and the only) singer of Nightwish. Included are two alternative versions of I Walk Alone. The others are Die Alive - the second single from My Winter Storm, and the earlier singles from the Finnish Christmas album Breath from Eternity: Happy New Year and You Would Have Loved This. The latter was sold only in Finland in a limited issue of 1000 copies. Enjoy this rare rip! Lossless of course. Also stay tuned for the new album. See Tarja touring this year!

I have a final announcement to make. I've had lots of fun providing you with cool stuff. Sadly, I won't be around much longer. I have seeded all my torrents up to now, but in the times to come it will be up to you to keep my torrents alive. I hope you have enjoyed my many uploads during the past several months and will continue to do so. Kopimi and enjoy life! Live long and prosper.
